Imperial Capital would be in the
hands of the enemy.

255
00:15:44,166 --> 00:15:47,466
[PINA] Our citizens taken as
their slaves.

256
00:15:47,566 --> 00:15:50,433
[HAMILTON] But they'd never...!
[PINA] Are you sure of that?

257
00:15:50,533 --> 00:15:52,000
You think they helped
us rescue this town

258
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:53,233
just to give it back?

259
00:15:54,933 --> 00:15:56,266
[PINA] I don't have the power to
refuse

