266
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,333
a fair and equitable
compensation.

267
00:16:13,433 --> 00:16:16,233
[HAMILTON] Article Two,
is regarding all envoys...

268
00:16:16,333 --> 00:16:17,700
and their safe passage,

269
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,166
as well as all their expenses...

270
00:16:19,266 --> 00:16:20,733
[HAMILTON] And Article Three
is regarding

