273
00:16:24,733 --> 00:16:27,000
[HAMILTON] However, we would
like to make it clear

274
00:16:27,100 --> 00:16:28,600
that we possess
the right to captives.

275
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:30,833
[LELEI] We understand that human
resources

276
00:16:30,933 --> 00:16:32,766
are necessary for Italica's
recovery.

277
00:16:32,866 --> 00:16:35,166
[LELEI] However...
they want assurance

