[LELEI] This is their
requirement.

286
00:16:55,766 --> 00:16:57,100
[HAMILTON] Hmm Very well then...

287
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,166
that will be all regarding
treatment of the captives.

288
00:16:59,266 --> 00:17:02,633
[HAMILTON] The rest of the
provisions address conditions
for withdrawal of your troops.

289
00:17:02,733 --> 00:17:05,233
[LELEI] No objections as it's
been written.

290
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,033
(query)

291
00:17:08,700 --> 00:17:10,666
[HAMILTON] Then the terms have
been agreed upon.

292
00:17:10,766 --> 00:17:12,100
