the city limits.

339
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:16,013
[RYUDO] Aha! Privileged merchant
status isn't easy to come by.

340
00:19:16,113 --> 00:19:21,113
Well, I'd normally give you 200
gold and 4000 denari silver for
such a prize.

341
00:19:21,213 --> 00:19:24,080
The thing is... what with the
battle we just had in the city,

342
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,680
