343
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:29,246
[RYUDO] I can only give you
a thousand denari at the moment.

344
00:19:29,346 --> 00:19:33,480
[LELEI] And the rest?
[RYUDO] I can make out a draft
for 2,000 right away...

345
00:19:33,580 --> 00:19:35,880
