[ASSISTANT] Really?

352
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:51,146
They thought that was worth a
thousand?

353
00:19:51,246 --> 00:19:54,946
[RYUDO] That's the beautiful
thing about the trade business
my boy.

354
00:19:55,046 --> 00:19:56,280
[RYUDO] One man's rubbish

